"Lloro Por Ti" (Eng.: I Cry for You) is the second single released by Enrique Iglesias from his compilation album Enrique Iglesias: 95/08 Exitos. The song was released as an official single in July 2008.

Enrique Iglesias performed the Lloro Por Ti on July 17, 2008 in Premios Juventud along with Aventura.

The Music video premiered on 6 of July of 2008.
